{"tid":1698573,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【區選】國家隊𠝹票 2.0","createTime":"2019-11-07T14:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T15:34:12.000Z","uid":337413,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f76a65c0b946ad83644ccdb87dc61c95baf76fa8","tid":1698573,"uid":337413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:46:40.000Z","msg":"尋晚個post 火速 1001, 先多謝手足關注, 今晚決定加料再 post  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>舊post :國家隊𠝹票</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696973/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696973/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n睇咗有位手足post 咗油尖旺有大陸仔𠝹票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696646/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696646/page/1</a>)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗你老味𠝹票撚肯定唔只一件<br />\n果然發現自己嗰區同附近有國家隊出來𠝹票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係小弟嘅 findings, 幫助大家判斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟發現有8條柒頭好可能係國家隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黃惠達</strong></span> (E05油尖旺-富榮)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>蔡其隆</strong></span> (E12 油尖旺-大南)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>葉智豪</strong></span> (F02 深水埗-長沙灣)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>王曉聖</strong></span> (F03深水埗-南昌北)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>林浩楠</strong></span> (F21深水埗-李鄭屋)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>林天恩</strong></span> (G01九龍城-馬頭圍)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李浩培</strong></span> (G18九龍城-鶴園海逸)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李進龍</strong></span> (G23九龍城-家維)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUuZbxF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUuZbxF.jpg&h=d01d3224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班死撚樣有以下共通點:<br />\n- 全部係柒頭武警公安撚樣, 資料又唔齊, 冇忽似香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 全鳩部提名日最後嗰日先報名, 明顯係𠝹票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 全部候選人簡介係用 PowerPoint template 做, 有冇咁啱先? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 全撚部 search 唔到官方 social media <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">===============================================</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黃惠達</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(E05油尖旺-富榮): <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">選油尖旺係都講831喇</span></strong>, 做乜講元朗721? 唔通本來assign 落元朗?<br />\n同區有民主黨 李偉峰 &amp; 民建聯 鍾港武<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G9eeKTf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG9eeKTf.jpg&h=3f346a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">蔡其隆</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (E12 油尖旺-大南): 根本係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">武警公安</span></strong>柒頭, 成條撚樣, 仲要填嘅名同banner 名唔match, 你係Choi Ki Lung 定 Choi Keng Lung ? 媽, 我好亂, 另外, 有手足補充蔡其隆係某快遞公司做, 講野有口音, 荔枝角出沒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BrDGpTH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBrDGpTH.jpg&h=c0588212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">葉智豪</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(F02 深水埗-長沙灣): PowerPoint 撻字style, 字體顏色好難睇, 專業少少好唔好? 個樣明明係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">送水佬</span></strong>, 點撚解要扮文員仔?<br />\n同區有長沙灣社區發展力量 李文浩 &amp; 經民聯 龐朝輝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKDjbzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKDjbzo.jpg&h=94185202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">王曉聖</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (F03深水埗-南昌北): <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幫民賤聯鄭泳舜助攻</span></strong>, 十惡補不赦, 同區有公民黨 劉家衡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fF019mk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfF019mk.jpg&h=754fef05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林浩楠</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (F21深水埗-李鄭屋): PowerPoint 又係撻字style, 字體顏色好難睇, 似十足葉智豪個 banner style , <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">外賣仔扮建造業</span></strong>, 專業少少好唔好? 仲有, 有手足影到林浩楠嘅單張 (post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696578/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696578/page/1</a> ) , 大家欣賞下佢嘅文采<br />\n同區有經民聯 陳鏡秋 &amp; 民協 江貴生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDWEbBk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDWEbBk.jpg&h=1d61e32d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fD5hHH3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfD5hHH3.jpg&h=d96d0fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林天恩</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (G01九龍城-馬頭圍) : 這是正式取錄的<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武警</span></strong>嗎? 負責駕駛軍車的司機嗎? 條撚樣gel 咗頭都洗唔走武警味囉<br />\n同區有 獨立 曾健超 &amp; 民建聯 邵天虹<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2f1EbBG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2f1EbBG.jpg&h=9fadcabc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">李浩培</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(G18九龍城-鶴園海逸): 這是正式取錄的武警嗎? 負責批發武器嗎? 你以為叫自己做Patrick 就無人知你係國家隊? Banner 內容抄林天恩, 專業少少好唔好?多謝手足補充, 條撚樣個名同 banner 唔match, 好求鳩其<br />\n同區有 民主黨 郭天立 &amp; 自稱獨立余志榮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Muf5RBZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMuf5RBZ.jpg&h=131740a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李進龍</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(G23九龍城-家維): <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大陸柒味</span></strong>濃到爆炸, 同蔡其隆都係自稱做物流 (順X快遞?), 不論Banner 同件 Polo 嘅 style 都好撚似, 根本係一夥<br />\n同區有 民主黨 周熙雯 &amp; 自稱獨立 勞超傑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJiZV3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJiZV3Y.jpg&h=66b99b5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老味, Zoom 埋張車頭相睇, 發現<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">蔡其隆, 王曉聖, 林天恩,李進龍</span></strong>個眼神光係一鳩樣! 問過識影相嘅 friend, 佢話四個柒頭個眼光一定係同一燈光setting 先打到出來, 四個自稱無 &ldquo;政治聯繫&rdquo;, 去同一個studio影相, 有無咁啱阿?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6c2jV4R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6c2jV4R.jpg&h=2f2ef807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國家隊出來𠝹票係預咗, 齋係九龍我都搵到8件武警, <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位手足睇路</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">驅逐共狗 光復香港 時代革命</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221c6bf8333007e58eab158fe7277b0f7e83aff5","tid":1698573,"uid":337413,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:50:28.000Z","msg":"有個候選人背景好可疑, <strong>希望手足提供資料</strong>, 以下係我嘅分析:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PuaQ2L3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPuaQ2L3.jpg&h=804b64d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">方毅妍</span></strong> (G11 九龍城-龍城) 同區有獨立有 獨立馮達浚 &amp; 民建聯吳寶強。 雖然搵到facebook <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fongngaiyin/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffongngaiyin%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKzk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=6801c701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fongngaiyin/</a> , 但最近先開, 以區選計落區太遲, 加上10月15日先報名, 不免令人覺得係鬼,  加上我Zoom 埋睇 , 屌,原來同國家隊嘅眼神光一撚樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zNgdSS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zNgdSS.jpg&h=8fa8af1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5afeb2b6dd18a70ba463695454952790621598b7","tid":1698573,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"f92ca4b3387c63cbb9ae26dd85a0eb726fe1849b","tid":1698573,"uid":337413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"07d7baaf84e730733a098a0ebc8e35ecac44d095","tid":1698573,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"咩國家隊啊，打国家隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ad5f9b606b59a0157b5b729c32a5e62a7d7765","tid":1698573,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: 